&lt;P&gt;They are a rare drop from a HUGE amount of mobs.&amp;nbsp; So yes, there is no particular zone or mob to&amp;nbsp;go to to get&amp;nbsp;them.&amp;nbsp; Even if we only consider level 1-20 mobs, three are well over 450 possible mobs to get it from.&amp;nbsp; If you include all the possible mobs, regardless of level, I expect it to be nearing 10k possible mobs.&amp;nbsp; My data showed swamp of no hope as the best hunting ground from them, but it is probably only marginal, and even then I expect it to be frustratingly rare there.&amp;nbsp; It is something I plan to address when I am allocated time to work on the cultural drops.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
